      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations through benchmark test cases at MRL 2 level.",
      "rationale": "Code verification confirmed via standard benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step. Results match analytical and published reference solutions within expected numerical tolerances. Verification level adequate for MRL 2."
