    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. Quantitative output comparison demonstrates RH predictions within experimental uncertainty across all 5 COU operating points. Model is credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index acceptance criterion (RH < 1) provides a conservative safety margin relative to the predicate device benchmark.",
